,{"pid":"ee54c6fe23745d8a0d5f684c5e90eb6603c9b083","tid":600613,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f6ddf0889bfa52f8f4e0923f4922a15b94b077","tid":600613,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e91c6659bed9f81e22b126f502b8694a25f787fc","tid":600613,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"你老豆唔係親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"係親生，可立遺囑，果陣排公屋因爲我地二人入息加埋超左，所以間公屋無我名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"（B）死者遺下配偶及後裔<br />\n<br />\n如果死者遺下配偶及後裔，無論死者是否有父母或兄弟姊妹在生，死者的配偶可先取得以下遺產：<br />\n<br />\n死者所有的非土地實產；<br />\n剩餘遺產中的500,000元。<br />\n在上述的 500,000 元分發後，如果尚有剩餘之數，便會再分成兩半，一半分發給配偶，另一半則平均分發給死者的所有子女。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/probate/distribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties/q3.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2Fprobate%2Fdistribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties%2Fq3.shtml&d=%2FDtg%2F59PK1glyPu4UB1EgZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e2b8b377\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/probate/distribution_of_estate_to_the_relevant_parties/q3.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"bdf2bc158a983a2c9a51ca76ab11bdc02fdb1ee3","tid":600613,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9021b853f3416928cf657c03ca8eb7b503fd5f82","tid":600613,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"買居屋上律師樓個時加你名<br />\n無問題的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"用綠表買但張綠表無我名，咁都加得咩？"},{"pid":"05679156ae2aeb67133cede193e54ae76d11bcaa","tid":600613,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"推鳩"},{"pid":"930041988389d0151bab3509975849382ee62020","tid":600613,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"推鳩